    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> With this proposal, the left operand would always be a GroupBy object and the right operand would always be a the result of a function application against that same GroupBy.\r\n\r\nIt would be surprising not to also support the other order, e.g., `other + groupby`. This should be totally doable, though."
