    "body": "This already is the idiomatic way, quite explict.\r\n\r\n```\r\nIn [3]: df.val - df.groupby('key').val.transform('mean')\r\nOut[3]: \r\n0   -0.5\r\n1    0.5\r\n2   -0.5\r\n3    0.5\r\nName: val, dtype: float64\r\n```"
