    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Another use case is when the normalization values are pre-computed, perhaps from another dataset, e.g.,  you only have access to`df.groupby('key').mean()`. You can certainly still apply these in pandas, but it requires explicit reindexing or merging."
